00:57:01,210 --> 00:57:04,797
Rep don't carry over
from decade to decade.

1206
00:57:04,880 --> 00:57:06,507
Tired-ass 1940s slang you using.

1207
00:57:06,590 --> 00:57:07,842
That was definitely
not hep, daddy-o.

1208
00:57:07,925 --> 00:57:09,009
Talking about "blew your wig."

