00:57:11,220 --> 00:57:14,807
Fine, just stop joking
for a second.

1211
00:57:14,890 --> 00:57:15,975
Okay.

1212
00:57:17,268 --> 00:57:18,477
Jesus.

1213
00:57:21,147 --> 00:57:22,982
SAM and JIM:
"You blew your wig."

